{"_path":"/councilor/service/s2015","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"爭取樂善二路不強制待轉","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s2015-1.jpeg","sequence":2015,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/TYleehao/","author":"李宗豪","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"李宗豪"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-02-29T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"爭取樂善二路不強制待轉"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"爭取樂善二路不強制待轉"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"解除限制 🛵 樂善二路拆除機車待轉牌，全路口不強制兩段式左轉！\n宗豪在去年 11 月中旬時，到樂善二路與樂善里黃錦芳里長共同會勘，順利將本路段數個路口的機車待轉牌取消，也在近日正式完成拆除！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"未來「樂善二路」沿途幾個路口將「不強制待轉」，可以自由選擇提早靠左直接左轉，或者是靠右行至機車待轉區等待，增加交通的便利性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在宗豪的爭取下，樂善二路為不強制待轉的先行試辦路段，若未來交通運作順暢，希望能將「不強制待轉」推動至其他路口。\n繼續朝更友善的交通環境努力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s2015-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s2015-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"爭取樂善二路不強制待轉","depth":2,"text":"爭取樂善二路不強制待轉"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s2015.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s2015.md","_extension":"md"}